festival.introText:
The Hastings Reggae Festival

The BIGGEST EVER family friendly Reggae show to hit East Sussex. Come and join us for a celebration of ALL things Reggae!

If you would like to apply for a personal assistant ticket, please click here help.skiddle.com
festival.descriptionText: Skiddle is an official ticket outlet of Hastings Reggae Festival 2023. Get Hastings Reggae Festival 2023 tickets, news and information with Skiddle.com

faqs.question: Does Hastings Reggae Festival have onsite camping?
faqs.answer: No, this is a non-camping festival so camping equipment is not needed. It is however close to the City Centre and so there is plenty of alternative accommodation to choose from.

faqs.question: When is Hastings Reggae Festival 2023?
faqs.answer: Hastings Reggae Festival takes place on Saturday 29th July 2023.

faqs.question: Are pre-payment plan tickets available?
faqs.answer: No, there aren't any payment plans available for this event.

faqs.question: Where is Hastings Reggae Festival?
faqs.answer: Hastings Reggae Festival takes place at The Oval, Hastings. Bohemia Rd, Hastings TN34 1EU

faqs.question: What happens If I bought a ticket and cannot attend?
faqs.answer:
Unfortunately we can’t issue you with a refund if you can’t make the event due to work commitments or your mates have dropped out. In these circumstances, we advise passing on your tickets privately to avoid losing out on the money spent.

 

Refunds can only be offered if the event is cancelled or postponed, as agreed upon purchase

faqs.question: What is included in a VIP ticket?
faqs.answer: A VIP ticket includes access to VIP area, VIP toilets & bar, and queue jump.

faqs.question: Does Hastings Reggae Festival have any age restrictions?
faqs.answer: There is no age limit, however all children up to the age of 17 MUST be accompanied by an adult.
